{
  "stem": "3453.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I told them who I was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, OK, we'll put you into bins.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember she took us out in the field and she hide us for a day or two.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then and then we decided, with my sister, that we'll go to Karasin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Karasin was away from the town, deep in the woods.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Right already, it-- it's more White Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's into-- deep into the woods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And down there we have a more chance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We heard in the ghetto there are-- there are Partisans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There are rumors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All kind of rumors were going around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there, where we decide-- I said to my sister, we are going to that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We are going down there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one night, we went at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And everything at night had to be done.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember at night, we were going by a little stream, by a little river.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at night, I heard on the other side of the-- of the stream people are washing their hands, and I got so-- I became so excited, so happy.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I thought this must be people like ours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I wanted to speak out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But then, you know, intuitively sometimes-- I said to my sister, quiet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Let's hear what's going on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were thieves going out at night, and going out to my village, where my family lived, coming out with some honey, some things-- some honey and some-- some other goodies.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Who knows.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And one to the other one said in Ukrainian, let's get up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Let's go from here, because it's daybreak is coming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then I find out that they were actually thieves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But the ironic things, you know, the-- the thieves and the things sometimes used to help those unfortunate people, us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
